"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-olympics-2024-giorgia-villa-parmesan-cheese-b2590004.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  'Could it be more Italian than this?'\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Giorgia Villa has become the latest breakout star from theParis 2024Olympics, and not just because she helpedItalyscore its first-ever team gymnastics medal.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 385, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather, it's because the Olympian was at one point sponsored by none other than parmesancheese.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999946069238, \"rank\": 5.392902505570235e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the women's gymnastics all-around final on Tuesday, fans were quick to learn that the 21-year-old gymnast was previously sponsored by Parmigiano Reggiano.\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 784, \"end\": 803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parmigiano Reggiano\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I need the people to know that Olympic silver medalist Giorgia Villa is sponsored by parmesan cheese and regularly posts pics of herself with giant wheels of cheese,\\\" one userwroteon X, formerly Twitter, on July 31.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\"}, {\"begin\": 1001, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0469797065459847e-19, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one viral photo shared online, Villa posed in her gymnastics leotard and hugged a giant wheel of parmesan cheese, as she pretended to eat a block in a second image.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another snap from Parmigiano Reggiano showed Villa sitting on top of three wheels of cheese.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parmigiano Reggiano\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympic silver medalist Giorgia Villa sponsored by Parmigiano Reggiano,\\\" another X user said.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\"}, {\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parmigiano Reggiano\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Could it be more Italian than this?\\\"\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Giorgia Villa is really out here living all our dreams,\\\" someone else wrote.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa was named the latest ambassador for the parmesan cheese brand in 2021, shortly after she won the bronze medal at the 2019 World Championships and took home gold at the 2022 Mediterranean Games and the 2022 European Championships.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A new face is added, as a testimonial, to the prestigious team of Parmigiano Reggiano: the young gymnast Giorgia Villa, 2018 champion of the Youth Games and one of the most promising athletes in her specialty at an international level,\\\" Italian marketing agency Impresa e Sport announced in apress release, translated to English.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parmigiano Reggiano\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\"}, {\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Villa\"}, {\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.999681279686015, \"rank\": 0.00026850156286384536, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tenacious, determined, smiling, Giorgia proudly underlined this new role as well as once again confirming how the combination of Parmigiano Reggiano and the world of sport is indissoluble in terms of authenticity, quality and energetic value, both in sporting activity and in correct nutrition.\\\"\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2196, \"end\": 2215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parmigiano Reggiano\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking toInstagram, Villa shared that she was \\\"very happy\\\" to be a new member of the Parmigiano Reggiano family.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since I was a child, I have always loved this amazing product, a symbol of excellence and Italian culture, and since today being able to collaborate with them makes me extremely proud and excited to face future challenges!\\\"\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2568, \"end\": 2583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Italy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Italian culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"the Olympic athlete captioned her post in April 2021.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it's unclear if Villa is still an official sponsor of the cheese brand, as she has not posted a cheese-themed photo on social media since 2022.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa is not the only viral figure to emerge from the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American gymnastStephen Nedoroscik was deemed \\\"Clark Kent\\\" by the internetfor his skills on the pommel horse, which helped the US men's gymnastics team land its first Olympic medal since 2008.\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2986, \"end\": 2994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999817281105104, \"rank\": 1.3441186384309327e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3033, \"end\": 3043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Superman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2191792110332745e-27, \"text\": \"Clark Kent\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Superman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Superman\"}, {\"begin\": 3113, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9849969257171627, \"rank\": 0.01502322451697112, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, rugby starIlona Maher has become TikTok's latest obsessionfor her Love Island-themed content in the Olympic VIllage and her important messages of body positivity.\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3290, \"end\": 3305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.114218350132532e-13, \"text\": \"Olympic VIllage\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Independenthas contacted Villa and Parmigiano Reggiano for comment.\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parmigiano Reggiano\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parmesan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3478, \"end\": 3489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1315473456334686e-15, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"